  "3133810": {
    "name": "Fine Work: Act I Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3133810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/9306d6ccc47b4c0134d793418be8e6b4.avif?t=1754393478\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras_big/9306d6ccc47b4c0134d793418be8e6b4.avif?t=1754393478 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Fine Work: Act I</i> is the first in a Slice-of-Life Romantic Mystery series, featuring cute clients, scheming gods, sentient cities, wild concerts, and weaving dreams.</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re just getting settled in the city of Gleamhold, and your workshop opens tomorrow. Sure, it's nice here, this cozy corner of a big, weird universe. But your <i>new clients</i> hail from distant dreams, bringing their own strange dramas to your doorstep. One and all, they seek <i>sendshape</i>: artifacts woven from the stuff of memory. And you don’t intend to disappoint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fine Work has mushroom mail, memory swapping, celeb dog-blobbers, undercity fight clubs, and a conch-shaped obelisk that eavesdrops on citizens…<i>what more could you ask for?</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dazzle Your Patrons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know Gleamhold’s otherworldly residents, and win them over with your artistic prowess (or, you know,<i> just being friendly</i>). You’ll grow close to your clients over late night gossip, underground escapades, drinks at the Hobby Lantern, long walks, and exploring memories while<i> sendshaping</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/b74009248dc56e69dd090d7b7158e872.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/b74009248dc56e69dd090d7b7158e872.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/b74009248dc56e69dd090d7b7158e872.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weave the Dream</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft beautiful, bespoke artifacts with relaxing musical gameplay. Explore your clients’ memories in a surreal 3D dreamscape as you perfect your trade. Each client brings their own distinct musical style, be it foley-driven electronica, sword-fight breakcore, or baroque chamber tunes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/ac38b4519e48fd2a318c1b12b087881c.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/ac38b4519e48fd2a318c1b12b087881c.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/ac38b4519e48fd2a318c1b12b087881c.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a Living City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gleamhold is a growing city, with lots to discover! By day or night, from public squares to secret underground reaches, each cinemagraphic environment changes with the time of day, season, and happenings within the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/e80374a431691fee521372bca103c32a.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/e80374a431691fee521372bca103c32a.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/e80374a431691fee521372bca103c32a.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spin Your Own Tale</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With six starting traits to choose from + branching paths and hidden intrigues, no two playthroughs will be the same. Are you Charming? Discerning? Graceful or Mighty? Your choices now will change the future of Gleamhold and its strange inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/53a5fef71920b5e870b6ebea77aee1f4.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/53a5fef71920b5e870b6ebea77aee1f4.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/53a5fef71920b5e870b6ebea77aee1f4.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dive Into the Lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock collectable notebook entries as you record the sights, sounds, and otherworldly denizens of Gleamhold. Different secrets and deep cuts are hidden throughout the branching narrative paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/45ea265d9098693cf5f4e0dfce7efd7a.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/45ea265d9098693cf5f4e0dfce7efd7a.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/45ea265d9098693cf5f4e0dfce7efd7a.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo Content/Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   In the<strong> Fine Work Demo</strong>, you'll experience your first 3 days as a shaper in Gleamhold. In these early days, you can: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open your shop and meet the varied denizens of Gleamhold</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your hand at the loom in four musical 3D crafting levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather notes about the world and the strange beings therein</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore some of the city's varied locales<br> <br> <strong>The Fine Work Demo is best played on mouse and keyboard! Controller Support and Steam Deck Support are WIP, and may not function as expected. Assets and features seen in the demo are still in development/subject to change.</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/82c119536839ac0677cdc3b22f1e57a4.poster.avif?t=1754393478\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/82c119536839ac0677cdc3b22f1e57a4.webm?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133810/extras/82c119536839ac0677cdc3b22f1e57a4.mp4?t=1754393478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Find us @fineworkgame on all socials!</h2>",
